mainText: Matthew Chapter 11, Verse 28 - Come unto me, all ye that labour and are heavy laden, and I will give you rest.
Philippians Chapter 4, Verse 19 - But my God shall supply all your need according to his riches in glory by Christ Jesus.
Psalm 37, Verse 39 - But the salvation of the righteous is of the Lord: he is their strength in the time of trouble.
Psalm 46, Verse 1 - God is our refuge and strength, a very present help in trouble.
Psalm 46, Verse 10 - Be still, and know that I am God
